description: Amy Grant – Greatest Videos 1986-2004 [2004] DVD5 This is a collection of Amy's videos from 1986 to 2004. The videos from the albums 'The Collection', 'Lead Me On', and 'Heart In Motion' are included and were superb videos during their release that got heavy rotation on VH1, MTV, etc. These are the best videos on the dvd. The videos from the album 'House Of Love' lacked in production even during their time of release and never got much rotation on VH1, MTV, etc. The video from her duet with Peter Cetera "Next Time I Fall" was a hit on MTV back in its day. The video for "Simple Things", which was never picked up by VH1 or MTV, but nicely done, is also included. Amy's commentary, on the videos, is included.
